## Problem 4.3

Note for $x < 0$
$$
x_+^{\I \beta} = \E^{\I \beta \log_+ x} = \E^{\I \beta \log_- x - 2\pi \beta} = \E^{-2 \pi \beta} x_-^{\I \beta}
$$
```julia
